  <brief_title>Follow-up of Serum Androgen Profile After Bariatric Surgery in Men With Obesity Related Hypogonadotropic Hypogonadism</brief_title>
  <official_title>Follow-up of Serum Androgen Profile After Bariatric Surgery in Men With Obesity Related Hypogonadotropic Hypogonadism</official_title>
